  <notes>
    - Follow Api/Ai/AnalysisEndpoints.cs for AI endpoint structure and PlaybookService usage
    - Follow Services/Spe/SpeFileStore.cs for file upload patterns — understand upload method signatures
    - File content can be passed to AI as base64 or via file references (depends on PlaybookService API)
    - The AI prompt should instruct structured JSON output for reliable field extraction
    - Budget extraction should handle various formats: "$1,000,000", "1M", "one million dollars"
    - Practice area mapping should normalize AI output to the dropdown options defined in the form
    - Consider extracting key parties as a comma-separated list or structured array
    - If AI Playbook times out, return empty PreFillResponse with confidence=0 (no error)
    - The temporary file storage path should be cleaned up after the matter is created (or after a timeout)
    - Multipart form data handling in Minimal API: use [FromForm] attribute or IFormFileCollection parameter
  </notes>

